Author: Astronautee
Text: Oh my gosh I cant believe anyone actually read that long ass post, im really thankful right now ;; And yeah I did goto the hospital but they found no problems, I found more problems at the dentist.. (rip 4k) And thank you so much :) im trying my best to stay away from mpa/pancake/edc whatever but its so hard to haha I really appreciate the concern, its hard irl and this made my day. Again, thank you so much and I hope youre taking care of yourself too!!!

Author: Kitizen
Text: Hey, I remember reading your post on MPA/MPA2! I couldn't stop worrying about whether you had gone to the hospital or not. I'm glad that you're still striving towards recovery. You deserve to be healthy and happy!  Take care, and keep it up!
